00:04:22.759 --> 00:04:26.139
things and have their friends be able to find
them in a way that's meaningful to them, is

00:04:26.139 --> 00:04:30.789
very important. On the flip side of that when
people are surprised by information being

00:04:30.789 --> 00:04:35.139
shared that they hadn't necessarily anticipated
being found by certain people, then that creates

00:04:35.139 --> 00:04:39.550
a tension and erodes trust. So one of the
hardest things that we're having to deal with

00:04:39.550 --> 00:04:44.740
now in general and I, I say we as in the industry
is coming up with interaction models that

00:04:44.740 --> 00:04:50.039
