the tail end of the dot-com bubble. And if

00:08:26.069 --> 00:08:30.430
you remember back then everyone was absolutely
beside themselves with fear with this whole

00:08:30.430 --> 00:08:35.530
notion of a "cookie". And that you might be
attachable to what you're doing online. And

00:08:35.530 --> 00:08:40.599
