00:09:42.649 --> 00:09:43.649
&gt;&gt;Chris Cole: and among other things.

00:09:43.649 --> 00:09:44.649
&gt;&gt;Kara: Oh, those pedophiles.

00:09:44.649 --> 00:09:45.649
&gt;&gt;Chris Cole: And we've cleaned up a lot of
