00:44:45.079 --> 00:44:52.599
give permission to third parties if you don't
know who they are.

00:44:52.599 --> 00:45:03.279
&gt;&gt;Ryan: Well, well, and so we, I go about
that the other way. I think trying to give

00:45:03.279 --> 00:45:17.499
the granular permissions to apps up-front
